Class CustomException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.alternacraft.pvptitles.Exceptions.CustomException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DBException, RanksException

    public abstract class CustomException
extends Exception
    Custom exception.
      This add some extras:
    • Structured messages
        There are three type:
      • Simplified. Just for indicating an error
      • Essential. Essential information for finding a reason
      • Full. Complete error
    • How to report
    • Functionality for finding a possible reason of the error
    Author:
    AlternaCraft
